========

EXPLANATION
BY THE LEGISLATIVE COUNCIL
OF
A N A C T
RELATING TO SOLEMNIZATION OF MARRIAGES
***
1 This act would allow Joseph Couto to join Brandon Kemmy and Jacqueline Manousos in
2 Marriage on or about August 2, 2026, within the Town of Tiverton, Rhode Island.
3 This act would take effect upon passage.
